metadata.title: RA Family: What is DSpotter and DSpotterNLU?

sections.content:
Question:
What is DSpotter and DSpotterNLU?
Answer:
Both are cloud based Voice Recognition AI model development tool provided by Cyberon.
DSpotter: https://www.renesas.com/us/en/products/microcontrollers-microprocessors/ra-cortex-m-mcus/ra-partners/cyberon-dspotter
DSpotterNLU: https://www.renesas.com/us/en/products/microcontrollers-microprocessors/ra-cortex-m-mcus/ra-partners/cyberon-dspotternlu
Suitable Products
RA8M1
